## 1. DEVICE IDENTIFICATION:
id: siemens-s7-1200-cpu-1214c
name: "Siemens SIMATIC S7-1200 CPU 1214C DC/DC/DC — Compact PLC, 100KB work memory, 14 DI 24VDC, 10 DO MOSFET 24VDC 0.5A, 2 AI 0-10V, 6xHSC 100kHz, 4xPTO 100kHz, PROFINET, Modbus TCP, OPC UA, 3 CM + 8 SM + 1 SB expansion"
manufacturer: "Siemens AG"
mcu: "Siemens proprietary CPU 1214C DC/DC/DC — 0.085µs bit op; 1.7µs word op; 2.5µs FP; RTC w/480h supercap backup; 4MB load flash; 100KB work RAM; IEC61131-3 LAD-FBD-SCL"
category: plc
image: siemens-s7-1200-cpu-1214c.svg
url: "https://www.siemens.com/global/en/products/automation/systems/industrial/plc/simatic-s7-1200.html"

