## 3. ELECTRICAL PROFILE (POWER PINS):
# Format: name | direction | voltage | type
# DC/DC/DC: 24VDC supply L+/M, range 20.4-28.8VDC, max 1.5A input
# 1L+/1M: DO supply rail — connected to same 24VDC source as CPU on DC/DC/DC variant
# SENS_L+/SENS_M: 24VDC sensor/encoder supply output, max 300mA, built-in short-circuit protection
# PE: Protective Earth — connect to DIN rail; recommended for DC variants; mandatory for CE/EMC compliance
powerPins[9|]{name|direction|voltage|type}:
  BOARD_L_PLUS|input|"24V"|null
  BOARD_M|null|null|ground
  PE|null|null|ground
  SENS_L_PLUS|output|"24V"|null
  SENS_M|null|null|
  1_M|null|null|ground
  2_M|null|null|ground
  3_L_PLUS|output|"24V"|null
  3_M|null|null|ground

## 4. GPIO MAP:
# Format: pin | type | pwm | int | label | roles
# DI Ia.0-Ia.5: 24VDC; HSC 100kHz single-phase / 80kHz diff; filter 0.1µs-20ms; isolation 707VDC; 50m shielded
# DI Ia.6-Ib.5: 24VDC; standard; 30kHz HSC; filter 0.2-12.8ms; 500m shielded / 300m unshielded
# DO Qa.0-Qa.3: MOSFET 24VDC 0.5A; PTO up to 100kHz; no overcurrent protection
# DO Qa.4-Qb.1: MOSFET 24VDC 0.5A; Qa.4 max 20kHz PTO; no overcurrent protection
# AI AIW0/AIW2: 0-10VDC; 10-bit (0-27648); 625µs/ch; no isolation from CPU; max 100m shielded
